org.jetel.ctl

Class NavigatingVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.ctl.NavigatingVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SyntheticNodeVisitor, TransformLangParserVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ASTBuilder, CodePieceExtractor.PositionedCodeVisitor, CTLTransformUtils.CtlAssignmentFinder, FindFunctionVisitor, TranslatingVisitor, TypeChecker

    public class NavigatingVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements TransformLangParserVisitor
    Default implementation of visitor pattern for AST tree generated by TransformLangParser. Automatically descends down the tree visiting every node on the way.
